import React from "react" import { useFormikContext } from "formik" import { CardContent, Typography, Box } from "@material-ui/core" import { Divider } from "@mui/material" export default function FormReview() { const itemsArray = [] const { values } = useFormikContext() const array = Object.entries(values) console.log(array) itemsArray.push( values.firstName, values.lastName, values.email, values.age, values.company, values.address1, values.address1, values.address2, values.city, values.province, values.postalcode ) // console.log(values) return ( Review Details {itemsArray.map((item, index) => { return (
First Name: {item}
) })} {/* First Name: {values.firstName} Last Name: {values.lastName} Email: {values.email} Age: {values.age} Company: {values.company} Address 1: {values.address1} Address 2: {values.address2} City: {values.city} Province: {values.province} Postal Code: {values.postalcode} */} ) }
